{"id":"ec7586f8-f495-4351-98a2-fcece7253b99","name":"Cult of the Lamb RPG","description":"<p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/63a88fdf-0173-45aa-a5e5-cbb20b5944ff_2d261350-0e76-4c64-b1c9-2d7dc9799352.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 3, 3)\"><strong>𝙳𝚘𝚗'𝚝 𝚢𝚘𝚞 𝚠𝚊𝚗𝚝 𝚝𝚘 𝚋𝚎𝚌𝚘𝚖𝚎 𝚊 𝚌𝚞𝚕𝚝 𝚕𝚎𝚊𝚍𝚎𝚛?</strong></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/63a88fdf-0173-45aa-a5e5-cbb20b5944ff_1fb64c00-a3c0-40a2-a3af-77c4538fb2d6.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">\"𝕱і᥎ᥱ ᑲᥱᥴ᥆mᥱs 𝖿᥆ᥙr ᑲᥱᥴ᥆mᥱs 𝗍һrᥱᥱ ᑲᥱᥴ᥆mᥱs 𝗍ᥕ᥆ ᑲᥱᥴ᥆mᥱs ᥆ᥒᥱ ᑲᥱᥴ᥆mᥱs ᥒ᥆𝗍һіᥒg.\"</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/63a88fdf-0173-45aa-a5e5-cbb20b5944ff_27cd77ed-cdf9-44fb-9ee8-e5f08460b915.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/77bd76eb-a2e9-4f45-9900-3cdb4351301f_character-cult-of-the-goat-rpg\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">[Jump into the Mirror World?]</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Shamura foresees the return of The One Who Remains Waiting, prophecies of the old faith travel through the land, but what about the unspoken prophecies?</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">What about, <strong>YOUR</strong> prophecy?</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/63a88fdf-0173-45aa-a5e5-cbb20b5944ff_99fbeb68-e321-4fea-aa8d-c17bbab1f4ca.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Explore the lands of the Old Faith, create your own cult, bound others to your will... or dont, and be bound by someone else's will</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Yaaaay, finally finished it, just so you all are aware, things may not always work correctly due to the quantity of tokens, so you should take the wheel sometimes</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Safe travels, and may The Lamb bless you</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">-&gt;Set before the events of the main game</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/63a88fdf-0173-45aa-a5e5-cbb20b5944ff_b2828c88-0444-4ebe-af07-318dce33c957.webp?width=1000\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScqX-ORyug6ojRcUMVBdAFGeTiL4nDuSxAzhBHFK1zP4uhE4w/viewform?usp=sf_link\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">[REQUEST BOTS]</a></h2>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"63a88fdf-0173-45aa-a5e5-cbb20b5944ff_9fb383a4-74d7-4903-b9df-e7ec9a9e4939.webp","creator":"V33-N0C3D4","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["🎮 Game","🪢 Scenario","🎲 RPG","⛪ Religion"],"chats":5006,"messages":148710,"created_at":"2024-08-07T03:25:53.864785+00:00"}